{"tid":199364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲航空飛香港客機　降落失速急墜釀15傷","createTime":"2017-04-13T06:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T03:59:01.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da72b0d65ed7494a12d3306ca8164bee00d37319","tid":199364,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170413/bkn-20170413135914520-0413_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170413%2Fbkn-20170413135914520-0413_00822_001.html&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=ef82a3c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170413/bkn-20170413135914520-0413_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲航空公司(Qantas Airways)一架由墨爾本飛往香港的客機，上周五(7日)即將降落之際，突然失速及急墜，機師緊急將自動控制切換為手動操縱，最終安全降落香港，事故導致機上15名乘客受輕傷。有指客機當時是為了避開上方另一架距離過近的客機，而出現急墜。澳洲交通安全局今日(13日)表示，認為事故嚴重，將深入調查。<br />\n<br />\n肇事客機型號是波音747，航班編號是QF29。<span style=\"color: red;\">客機當日飛至香港東南110公里時，於2.2萬呎高空飛行，突然失速及急墜。</span>澳洲交通安全局今日表示，事發時響起了警號，機師的操縱手桿也猛烈搖晃，機師見狀立即把自動控制改為手動操縱。<br />\n<br />\n機上乘客、任職教師的根達爾(Jemma Gendall)憶起九霄驚魂時，仍猶有餘悸。她表示，客機失速及急墜前，曾猛烈搖晃，有部分行李自頭上的行李架掉下來，擊中其他乘客的頭部。根達爾稱：「事情十分恐怖，我們之前未曾遇上，乘客開始尖叫。當客機急降時，我們以為它不會停止，直至墜毀為止。」根達爾表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">機長當時透露是為了避開另一架客機，而緊急調整飛行高度。</span>她指出，倘回程再遇上同樣情況，便不會再乘搭澳航的客機。<br />\n<br />\n澳航事後表示，事故是由於氣流所致，客機約2分鐘後已回復正常。得悉澳洲交通安全局展開調查後，澳航也會展開內部調查。"},{"pid":"743addef136d01b50cceb6c574ac9afe6417377d","tid":199364,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:41:20.000Z","msg":"次次一上機就戴安全帶直到落機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ab6a904c456046e58a257e2d0f519236c37055","tid":199364,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次一上機就戴安全帶直到落機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要戴埋頭盔"},{"pid":"10717be4be36cc5fbcf7336f8de8fade76bc9135","tid":199364,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:03:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>機長當時透露是為了避開另一架客機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知關唔關嗰個「好可靠」嘅空管系統事呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a277eafd6b7c2205f2113d6f0eef648c3a62b4bf","tid":199364,"uid":37420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"88ba41838a3ca5ecea23a839b0d9ce5e0dbd3d27","tid":199364,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:15:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>機長當時透露是為了避開另一架客機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知關唔關嗰個「好可靠」嘅空管系統事呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>有指客機當時是為了避開上方另一架距離過近的客機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有可能"},{"pid":"fa38263cbaa4ebcc91570c9152f542e962766874","tid":199364,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>機長當時透露是為了避開另一架客機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知關唔關嗰個「好可靠」嘅空管系統事呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>有指客機當時是為了避開上方另一架距離過近的客機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有可能</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e81e023322e886da9b1533cb168e9c1f59014f","tid":199364,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:19:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>機長當時透露是為了避開另一架客機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知關唔關嗰個「好可靠」嘅空管系統事呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   咪傻啦  關咩事"},{"pid":"9b45923ea8a4fb894217829e5427917052e31278","tid":199364,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"避飛機點會失速<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccad5d2471272b7bd8da78d02a5ccac536605d24","tid":199364,"uid":87578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:26:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得其實個重點應該係點解要避飛機<br />\n會唔會係個陣無啦啦有架飛機隱形咗<br />\n控制塔唔知原來有兩架飛機嘅距離咁接近<br />\n要機師自己發現然後避？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad44cf3fb1f21b9835bcde73543f2a242568c2d","tid":199364,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得其實個重點應該係點解要避飛機<br />\n會唔會係個陣無啦啦有架飛機隱形咗<br />\n控制塔唔知原來有兩架飛機嘅距離咁接近<br />\n要機師自己發現然後避？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新空管系統多事故，其子系統亦「多災多難」。「抵港航機排序系統」（Arrival Manager，簡稱「AMAN」）至少發生三次故障，分別於去年11月18日、今年1月2日以及2月12日。民航處消息人士批評，每次故障須即時改用人手控制飛機進入本港空域次序，不但費時失事，前線人員亦都會因為工作量上升而增加出錯的機會。民航處承認新系統啟用至今AMAN曾三次故障，兩次涉及人為因素，但強調空管人員有能力應付。 <br />\n<br />\nAMAN的功能，是提供自動化的抵港航班排序資訊，輔助空管人員執行航班排序的工作，以提升航班準時抵港率，善用空域及跑道容量，以往獨立運作，現時則收納於新空管系統。 <br />\n<br />\n民航處指，首兩宗事故涉及人為因素，在2月12日的事故，處方承認系統一度無法顯示部分航班的排序資訊，須按當時運作情況及經驗訂定預設間距。民航處消息人士批評，AMAN每次故障「要馬上改用人手計算」，雖對安全沒直接影響，但每次均導致「天空比較亂」，亦增加空管人員的工作量。民航處補充，空管人員遇上AMAN故障時會嘗試重啟它，「絕對可應付這些情況」。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170410/mobile/bkn-20170410001304567-0410_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170410%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170410001304567-0410_00822_001.html&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=74026cd3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170410/mobile/bkn-20170410001304567-0410_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bee551cc4b8b7e01c45e7f7a5571091c6ace9c21","tid":199364,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:38:40.000Z","msg":"嘩，新空管系統十幾億喎<br />\nAman !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d97a27cd7166f51fe018485a300329bb7993fe","tid":199364,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩，新空管系統十幾億喎<br />\nAman !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒得成飛機嘅話 用多幾十億換個新嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b51ba5ff81894f6eaf702b259201b491bf841f3","tid":199364,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嘩，新空管系統十幾億喎<br />\nAman !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒得成飛機嘅話 用多幾十億換個新嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係唔怕生壞命，至怕改壞名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫Aman...Amen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過個空管本身都壞，有問題"},{"pid":"7a006c1cdbc3360f0df861e78c1fdb5d05d9ead9","tid":199364,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>嘩，新空管系統十幾億喎<br />\nAman !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒得成飛機嘅話 用多幾十億換個新嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係唔怕生壞命，至怕改壞名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫Aman...Amen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過個空管本身都壞，有問題</blockquote><br />\n就算炒獲大既, 成機人死係個別事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2e81d9e6ef91448473b3fbd7f4230929330367","tid":199364,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7bf427a09d15ab0cd922c6e84449565e8f6fce79","tid":199364,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:17:50.000Z","msg":"上面嗰班幽默感好多下"},{"pid":"c0350db97b3ed4296d579a1a275395494e3d88d0","tid":199364,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面嗰班幽默感好低下</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ae690757e4501699950ce4191dd0d5b6140a4132","tid":199364,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:18:56.000Z","msg":"照計避飛機都應該唔會避到Stall<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadeb6c13a141510e48655b44f63577d163f723d","tid":199364,"uid":33422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:21:09.000Z","msg":"其實應該係信tcas<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係嘅話民航處就要食屎"},{"pid":"ba81d3502876396132f0413e801b0b1a96fd42af","tid":199364,"uid":33682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照計避飛機都應該唔會避到Stall<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個就係問題之一<br />\n點解會STALL"},{"pid":"5daa56d2261e202a2cd20c61b63261ccc6365364","tid":199364,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:29:10.000Z","msg":"如果發生喺國泰航班上<br />\n東方會點報？"},{"pid":"46ffc1e061855943f5adcae205293644745cc791","tid":199364,"uid":80964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實應該係信tcas<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係嘅話民航處就要食屎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多人都唔知有TCAS 呢樣野<br />\n如果冇tcas，個新系統又死機就....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76b83e8c8679f85e26e111b7770c49ce142954b","tid":199364,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果發生喺國泰航班上<br />\n東方會點報？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因管理不善而更換行政總裁的國秦航公司，昨晚降落時失速，三百多人經歴九霄驚魂.....<br />\n<br />\n之後再搵幾條友話好撚驚，以後唔再搭因航<br />\n<br />\n又話咩因航機師訓練不足，維修又唔掂等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a9a166d08bb8e4cdcec7ae4789aa9f6244083f","tid":199364,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果發生喺國泰航班上<br />\n東方會點報？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因管理不善而更換行政總裁的國秦航公司，昨晚降落時失速，三百多人經歴九霄驚魂.....<br />\n<br />\n之後再搵幾條友話好撚驚，以後唔再搭因航<br />\n<br />\n又話咩因航機師訓練不足，維修又唔掂等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打好熟手"}]}